{
  "text": "The optimized lattice parameters for bulk TiO2 anatase are 3.789 \u00c5 and 3.766 \u00c5 for a and 9.777 \u00c5 and 9.663 \u00c5 for c, respectively, for B3LYP and HSE06, which are in good agreement with the experimental values [CITATION_1] .",
